  "check_in_html": "<b>Dave Polak</b> (770-356-5895)<br>Check in at <b>Litchfield Resort</b><br>14276 Ocean Blvd, Litchfield Beach, SC 29585<br>(843) 237-3000",
  "daily_announcements_html": "<p><b>Welcome to MBI 2026.</b> Check in Tuesday afternoon and bring cash for the kickoff dinner buy-in.</p>",
  "trip_schedule_html": "<div style=\"overflow:auto;\" class=\"table-responsive\"><table class=\"data-table\"><thead><tr><th>When</th><th>What</th><th>Where</th><th>Note</th></tr></thead><tbody>\n<tr><td>Tue : 5/13<br>4pm</td><td><b>Check in</b></td><td><i>Litchfield Resort</i></td><td>14276 Ocean Blvd<br>Litchfield Beach, SC 29585<br>(843) 237-3000</td></tr>\n<tr><td>Tue : 5/13<br>6pm</td><td><b>Kickoff dinner<br>and meeting</b></td><td><i>TPC Myrtle Beach<br>1199 TPC Blvd <br> Murrells Inlet, SC 29576</i></td><td>$200 cash buy-in. Bring cash (no $1 nor $5 bills) or Venmo @David-Polak-6.<br>This covers daily cash prizes, Tuesday\u2019s and Saturday night\u2019s dinner, taxes and tips.<br>For One-man, Two-day (@True Blue) Best Ball Tournament, pay Bill Matthews $20.</td></tr>\n<tr><td>Wed : 5/14<br>Morning</td><td><b>Golf</b></td><td><i>True Blue</i></td><td>First tee time, 8:06 AM. Off front and back</td></tr>\n<tr><td>Wed : 5/14<br>Evening</td><td><b>Dinner</b></td><td><i>On your own</i></td><td>#</td></tr>\n<tr><td>Thu : 5/15<br>Morning</td><td><b>Golf</b></td><td><i>TPC Myrtle Beach</i></td><td>First tee time, 8:00 AM. Off front and back</td></tr>\n<tr><td>Thu : 5/15<br>8pm</td><td><b>Dinner</b></td><td><i>Franks Outback restaurant</i></td><td>Dinner invitation (optional)</td></tr>\n<tr><td>Fri : 5/16<br>Morning</td><td><b>Golf</b></td><td><i>Heritage (optional)</i></td><td>First tee time, 9:00 AM. Off front and back</td></tr>\n<tr><td>Fri : 5/16<br>Evening</td><td><b>Dinner</b></td><td><i>On your own<br>(Russells Seafood for many)</i></td><td>#</td></tr>\n<tr><td>Sat : 5/17<br>Morning</td><td><b>Golf</b></td><td><i>Pawley\u2019s Plantation</i></td><td>First tee time, 9:21 AM. Off front and back</td></tr>\n<tr><td>Sat : 5/17<br>6pm</td><td><b>Awards banquet</b></td><td><i>Quigley\u2019s Next Door (QND)<br>257 Willbrook Blvd. P.I., SC 29585</i></td><td>Drinks at 6. Dinner about 7:00.<br>Dinner, taxes and tip are included in your $200. Drinks are not included.</td></tr>\n<tr><td>Sun : 5/18<br>Morning</td><td><b>Go home</b></td><td><i>Away</i></td><td>Hydrate!</td></tr>\n</tbody></table></div>",
